Testing Instructions:

  1. Access the demo interface:
  http://ip-172-31-44-30.compute-1.amazonaws.com:8080/static/demo.html
  2. Or run both services in parallel:
  # Terminal 1: Start WebSocket Bridge
  cd /opt/riva-ws
  python3 bin/riva_websocket_bridge.py

  # Terminal 2: Start HTTP Server (for demo interface)
  cd /home/ubuntu/event-b/nvidia-parakeet-ver-6
  python3 -m http.server 8080

  What You'll See:

  - Demo interface with microphone controls
  - Real-time connection status to WebSocket bridge
  - Live audio visualization of your microphone input
  - Real-time transcription results from RIVA's Parakeet RNNT model

  Testing Flow:

  1. Open the demo URL in a web browser
  2. Grant microphone permissions
  3. Click "Start Recording"
  4. Speak into your microphone
  5. See real-time transcription results appear




